OL,3,CAlmost 50 MPs to rebel over welfare
OL,4,Ccuts as Labour revolt grows
OL,6,FBy Senior Politics Producers Maya
OL,7,FBowles and Lili Donlon-Mansbridge
OL,9,FAlmost 50 Labour MPs are set to rebel
OL,10,Fagainst government plans to radically
OL,11,Fchange the welfare system, paving the
OL,12,Fway for the prime minister's biggest
OL,13,Frevolt yet.
OL,15,FITV News has been tracking how Labour
OL,16,FMPs plan to vote, and understands 49
OL,17,Fwill go against the government's plans
OL,18,Fto slash benefits for millions of
OL,19,Fpeople.
