OL,4,Ccuts as Labour revolt grows
OL,6,FDespite that, one senior Number 10
OL,7,Ffigure told ITV News' Deputy Political
OL,8,FEditor Anushka Asthana they feared up
OL,9,Fto 100 MPs could oppose the plans, and
OL,10,Fif the vote had happened last week in
OL,11,Fthe wake of the local elections, it
OL,12,Fwould likely inflict a bloody nose on
OL,13,FStarmer's administration.
OL,15,FMany Labour MPs have told ITV News
OL,16,Fthey're still deciding how to vote,
OL,17,Fand waiting to see the actual detail
OL,18,Fof the legislation they'll be voting
OL,19,Fon.
