OL,3,CAlmost 50 MPs to rebel over welfare
OL,4,Ccuts as Labour revolt grows
OL,6,FThere's no doubt the welfare vote is
OL,7,Flikely to see the biggest rebellion of
OL,8,FStarmer's premiership, and if all
OL,9,Fopposition parties vote against the
OL,10,Fplans, only 83 Labour MPs need to vote
OL,11,Fagainst the government to defeat the
OL,12,Flegislation.
OL,14,FIn a vote expected to take place in
OL,15,FJune, MPs will decide whether to pass
OL,16,Fthe Starmer's plans to shake up the
OL,17,Fwelfare system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
