OL,3,CAlmost 50 MPs to rebel over welfare
OL,4,Ccuts as Labour revolt grows
OL,6,FThe government plan to make it harder
OL,7,Ffor disabled people to claim Personal
OL,8,FIndependence Payments (Pip), and to
OL,9,Ffreeze universal credit incapacity
OL,10,Fbenefits for existing claimants, while
OL,11,Fcutting them by 50% for new claimants.
OL,13,FThe plans are expected to save #5bn
OL,14,Ffrom the ballooning welfare budget,
OL,15,Fbut critics warn the move will push
OL,16,Fvulnerable people into poverty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
