OL,6,FThe government's own impact assessment
OL,7,Fon the plans estimates that that in
OL,8,F2029-30, 3.2 million families will
OL,9,Flose an average of #1,720 a year as a
OL,10,Fresult of the cuts, with 250,000
OL,11,Fpeople pushed into relative poverty.
