OL,6,FThe Guardian newspaper also obtained
OL,7,Fgovernment forecasts last week that
OL,8,Fshowed the cuts will hit 700,000
OL,9,Ffamilies who are already in poverty,
OL,10,Fon top of the projected 250,000.
OL,12,FMany of the MPs who have come out in
OL,13,Fopposition to the plans are calling
OL,14,Ffor them to be delayed until the full
OL,15,Fassessment of cuts can be laid out,
OL,16,Fand for the consultation on the
OL,17,Fwelfare reform to be expanded to allow
OL,18,Fdisabled people and key stakeholders
OL,19,Fto engage in more detail.
