OL,3,CAlmost 50 MPs to rebel over welfare
OL,4,Ccuts as Labour revolt grows
OL,6,FOne Labour MP told ITV News: "I didn't
OL,7,Fbecome a Labour MP to make people
OL,8,Fpoorer", and was particularly critical
OL,9,Fof the Pip cuts, saying the government
OL,10,Fwere trying to sell a "cuts agenda as
OL,11,Freform".
OL,13,FAfter a disastrous set of local
OL,14,Felections for the government earlier
OL,15,Fthis month, an increasing number of
OL,16,Fbackbench Labour MPs have been warning
OL,17,Fthe government to change course not
OL,18,Fonly on the welfare cuts but also the
OL,19,Fcut to the winter fuel allowance for
OL,20,Fpensioners.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
