OL,6,FKendall insisted "being written off
OL,7,Fand having a life on benefits is not
OL,8,Fgood".
OL,10,FIn an interview with ITV News Digital
OL,11,FPolitical Reporter Lewis Denison,
OL,12,FDisability Minister Stephen Timms
OL,13,Ffailed to rule out coming back for
OL,14,Ffurther welfare cuts in the Autumn.
OL,16,F"There's lots of discussions going on
OL,17,Fat the moment, I'm very focused on the
OL,18,Fpackage we set out in March", he said.
